com.ibm.mq.badge

Class EventManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.ibm.mq.badge.EventManager

  • public class EventManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Deals with the creation and alterations of Event's. The EventManager also deals with the reading of data and the formatting of the data to be written.

    The EventManager also deals with processing requests such as ticket deductions for Events.

    Author:
    Benjamin Brunyee
    See Also:
